overview:
Search Engine Optimization Seattle (SEO) by pageSpike is an online management company based in Seattle WA. We specialize in getting your message out to your online audience through search engine optimization, paid search marketing, Pay Per Click, cohesive website design, social marketing and link building.

Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is the process of improving the volume and/or quality of traffic to your Web site from Search Engines. This is done on the unpaid area of the Search Engine, referred to as organic search results. We begin by analyzing your existing site, and from that develop a cohesive strategy for your target markets. Implementation is done through the use of highly-skilled optimizers armed with best-of-breed tools.

Local Optimization and Local search targeting is key for many businesses. Local searchers are more likely to convert to customers for businesses in their area. PageSpike can help you get to the top of your area.
